%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mark%20Cuban%20says%20the%20US%20has%20got%20to%20keep%20investing%20in%20research%20if%20it%20wants%20to%20have%20a%20chance%20of%20beating%20China%20at%20AI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mark%20Cuban%20is%20holding%20a%20microphone%20and%20speaking.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68996e5f194a2d49b8ae512b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223607%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20our%20Ph.D.s%2C%20our%20scientists%2C%20our%20experts%20to%20stay%20here%20and%20contribute%20to%20society%2C%20and%20their%20IP%20to%20make%20American%20AI%20models%20the%20global%20leaders%2C%26quot%3B%20Mark%20Cuban%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Sunday.%3Cp%3EJeff%20Schear%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMark%20Cuban%20says%20the%20US%20should%20not%20be%20paring%20down%20its%20research%20spending.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECuban%20said%20the%20work%20produced%20can%20be%20licensed%20to%20AI%20companies%20to%20enhance%20their%20models.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20this%20would%20offset%20research%20costs%20and%20keep%20the%20US%20ahead%20of%20China%20in%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShark%20Tank%26quot%3B%20star%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-why-he-started-cost-plus-drugs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMark%20Cuban%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20the%20US%20can%20beat%20China%20at%20AI%20if%20it%20continues%20%26quot%3Binvesting%20in%20research%20of%20all%20kinds%20as%20a%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20IP%20we%20create%20domestically%20is%20what%20the%20frontier%20models%20can%20buy%20or%20invest%20in%20to%20define%20their%20differentiation%20and%20advance%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20Cuban%20wrote%20on%20X%20in%20response%20to%20a%20post%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavid-sacks-chip-export-rules-weaken-us-tech-dominance-china-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDavid%20Sacks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20White%20House's%20AI%20and%20crypto%20czar%2C%20on%20the%20state%20of%20the%20AI%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20his%20X%20post%2C%20Cuban%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20American%20research%20is%20%26quot%3Bimportant%2C%20not%20just%20because%20of%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20research%20itself%2C%20but%20its%20value%20to%20American%20frontier%20AI%20models%26quot%3B%20like%20ChatGPT%20and%20Gemini.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECuban%20said%20that%20any%20unique%20intellectual%20property%20produced%20can%20be%20%26quot%3Blicensed%20to%20the%20models%2C%20for%20a%20fee%2C%20to%20be%20included%20in%20their%20training.%26quot%3B%20This%20would%20not%20only%20offset%20research%20costs%20but%20also%20make%20the%20models%20more%20valuable%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20quality%20and%20depth%20of%20the%20research%20we%20do%20in%20this%20country%20can%20help%20us%20stay%20ahead%20of%20China%20and%20other%20countries%20in%20the%20AI%20race%2C%26quot%3B%20Cuban%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20our%20Ph.D.s%2C%20our%20scientists%2C%20our%20experts%2C%20to%20stay%20here%20and%20contribute%20to%20society%2C%20and%20their%20IP%20to%20make%20American%20AI%20models%20the%20global%20leaders%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20taking%20office%20in%20January%2C%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20administration%20has%20been%20culling%20research%20grants%20for%20universities%20and%20research%20institutions%20like%20the%20National%20Institutes%20of%20Health%20(NIH).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20and%20scientists%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-research-funding-cuts-nobel-prizes-brain-drain-medicine-ai-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20Ayelet%20Sheffey%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April%20that%20the%20cuts%20could%20stifle%20innovation%20and%20result%20in%20bra