cleshow%2F123227284.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Built%20by%20a%20Sanskrit%20Scholar%20for%20his%20Polish%20Wife%2C%20This%20Uttarakhand%20Eco%20Stay%20is%20a%20Sustainable%20Paradise%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChestnut.%20Ringol.%20Oak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Jilling%20Terraces%2C%20the%20cottages%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20trees%20they%E2%80%99re%20named%20after%20%E2%80%94%20have%20long%20echoed%20a%20single%20message%3A%20sustainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20a%20theme%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20way%20of%20life%20here.%20It%20fills%20the%20air%2C%20shapes%20the%20architecture%2C%20nourishes%20the%20soil%2C%20seasons%20every%20meal%2C%20and%20colours%20every%20conversation%20between%20Sheela%20Venkatraman%20Lunkad%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20Rajeev.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20we%20join%20in%20the%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStraight%20out%20of%20a%20postcard%2C%20this%20eco%20stay%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20forests%20%E2%80%94%20100%20acres%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F329567%2Fmumbai-homestay-with-organic-farming-food-forest-sustainable-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekaleidoscopically%20diverse%20flora%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20has%20a%20backstory%20as%20beautiful%20as%20its%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELove%20has%20always%20been%20in%20the%20air%20at%20Jilling%20Terraces%3B%20its%20history%20proves.%20Sheela%E2%80%99s%20tale%20of%20one%20of%20the%20bungalows%2C%20Chestnut%20House%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20built%20in%201933%20by%20a%20Sanskrit%20scholar%20for%20his%20Polish%20doctor%20wife%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20case%20in%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20seems%20she%20was%20recommended%20the%20place%20for%20its%20cool%20climate%2C%20and%20so%20her%20husband%2C%20Subramanium%20Iyer%2C%20built%20her%20this%20cottage%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20Sheela%20and%20her%20family%20stumbled%20upon%20some%20tincture%20bottles%20one%20day%20during%20a%20spring%20cleaning%20session.%20This%20happened%20after%20they%20bought%20the%20land%20from%20Subramanium%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20Anant%20Ram%20Iyer%2C%20in%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discovery%20of%20the%20bottles%20supported%20their%20guess%20about%20Subramanium%E2%80%99s%20mother%E2%80%99s%20condition.%20They%20also%20believed%20that%20the%20change%20of%20scenery%20%E2%80%94%20with%20pockets%20of%20sunshine%20filtering%20through%20forests%20of%20tall%20Deodars%20and%20whispering%20pines%20%E2%80%94%20might%20have%20been%20a%20possible%20antidote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20land%20was%20meant%20to%20make%20her%20feel%20better.%20And%20it%20could%20do%20the%20same%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FJilling-Terraces-1754578896.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20tincture%20bottles%20that%20the%20family%20discovered%20(L)%20and%20Jilling%20Terraces%2C%20an%20eco%20stay%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20forests%20(R)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FJilling-Terraces-1754578896.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FJilling-Terraces-1754578896-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FJilling-Terraces-1754578896-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FJilling-Terraces-1754578896-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FJilling-Terraces-1754578896-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-483487%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ET