Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-old-house-renovation-before-after-japandi-kuala-lumpur-malaysia-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eliving%20in%20Malaysia%3C%2Fa%3E%20intermittently%20over%20the%20years%2C%20spending%20several%20months%20at%20a%20time%20taking%20it%20all%20in.%20It%20was%20also%20in%20Kuala%20Lumpur%2C%20the%20capital%20city%2C%20where%20I%20met%20my%20now-wife%2C%20Rachel%2C%20who%20is%20Malaysian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202023%2C%20I%20was%20offered%20a%20job%20with%20Melbourne%20Capital%20Group%2C%20a%20wealth%20management%20firm%2C%20in%20Kuala%20Lumpur.%20The%20visa%20process%20took%20around%20six%20months%2C%20and%20by%20January%20last%20year%2C%20I%20was%20fully%20settled%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228b0f1780-bb6a-417c-8b22-9b5d0fc1548c%5C%22%3EI%20realized%20I%20didn't%20really%20know%20anybody%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20moved%20around%20so%20much%20by%20then%2C%20and%20the%20longest%20I'd%20ever%20stayed%20in%20one%20place%20was%20two%20or%20three%20months.%20I%20didn't%20know%20who%20to%20ask%20about%20restaurants%2C%20or%20who%20to%20ask%20out%20for%20a%20drink%20when%20I%20finished%20work%20on%20a%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20had%20been%20to%20a%20few%20networking%20events%2C%20they%20were%20all%20really%20professional.%20You'd%20go%20there%2C%20and%20then%20you'd%20come%20home%20with%2010%20property%20agent%20business%20cards%20and%20five%20health%20insurance%20pamphlets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20came%20to%20the%20point%20where%20I%20thought%2C%20OK%2C%20I%20need%20to%20do%20something%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20joining%20an%20English%20society%2C%20but%20the%20problem%20with%20that%20was%20I'd%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebe%20surrounded%20by%20other%20English%20people.%20I%20didn't%20come%20to%20this%20side%20of%20the%20world%20just%20to%20meet%20English%20people%3B%20I%20wanted%20to%20meet%2