e3ed1%5C%22%3EThey%20all%20like%20different%20things%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20we%20have%20my%20husband's%20kids%20on%20the%20weekend%20and%20my%20own%20during%20the%20week%2C%20it%20involved%20a%20shuffling%20of%20schedules%20and%20coordinating%20with%20their%20other%20parents.%20We%20had%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworlds-most-scenic-road-great-coast-new-zealand-photos-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etake%20two%20vehicles%20and%20book%20accommodation%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20suit%20us%20all.%20The%2014-year-old%20certainly%20wasn't%20keen%20to%20share%20a%20room%20with%20a%20busy%204-year-old.%20Then%20there%20was%20the%20question%20of%20what%20activities%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20lucky%20in%20that%20our%20kids%20all%20get%20along%2C%20but%20they%20have%20very%20different%20ideas%20about%20what's%20fun%20to%20do%20on%20vacation.%20We%20spent%20our%20first%20day%20at%20the%20zoo%20and%20our%20second%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboston-cop-slide-viral-video-i-tried-it-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehuge%20outdoor%20playground%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Apart%20from%20the%204-year-old%20throwing%20her%20favourite%20toy%20out%20the%20car%20window%20and%20having%20to%20backtrack%20to%20hunt%20it%20down%2C%20everything%20went%20smoothly.%20The%20kids%20were%20happy.%20We%20were%20exhausted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Girl%20in%20playground%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68482c1285e81483682bc3a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20her%20husband%20plan%20trips%20around%20their%20kids'%20interests%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20our%20next%20trip%20away%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20make%20it%20simpler%20and%20only%20take%20the%20older%20three%2C%20but%20very%20quickly%2C%20our%20family%20vacation%20turned%20into%20two%20separate%20trips.%20My%20stepson%20wasn't%20keen%20to%20do%20any%20of%20the%20activities%20the%20older%20girls%20had%20in%20mind.%20He%20wanted%20to%20tour%20the%20parliament%20buildings%20and%20walk%20around%20the%20city%2C%20while%20the%20girls%20wanted%20to%20explore%20the%20museum%20and%20swim%20at%20the%20beach.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20made%20it%20work%2C%20but%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20trip%2C%20everyone%20was%20feeling%20a%20little%20frustrated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20took%20the%20younger%20three%20away%20together%2C%20we%20had%20a%20similar%20situation.%20They%20enjoyed%20staying%20at%20the%20unique%20tram%20carriage%20accommodation%2C%20but%20choosing%20what%20activities%20to%20do%20proved%20difficult.%20The%20girls%20loved%20visiting%20a%20wildlife%20park%2C%20but%20my%20stepson%20was%20miserable.%20As%20they've%20gotten%20older%2C%20their%20interests%20have%20separated%20even%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ff400cec-c9a3-4dfe-bbe3-c9be4bd5eda1%5C%22%3EIf%20we%20spend%20money%20on%20a%20trip%2C%20we%20want%20them%20to%20enjoy%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20we're%20going%20to%20spend%20time%20and%20money%20on%20a%20vacation%20for%20the%20kids%2C%20we%20want%20them%20to%20actually%20enjoy%20it%2C%20so%20this%20year%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20try%20something%20new.%20We'd%20take%20each%20child%20away%20by%20themselves.%20There'd%20be%20less%20coordination%20required%2C%20and%20we%20could%20tailor%20vacations%20to%20each%20child's%20interests.%20It%20also%20spreads%20out%20the%20costs%20over%20the%20year%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20much%20more%20doable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20my%20oldest%20daughter%2C%20now%20almost%2019%2C%20away%20for%20a%20girls'%20retreat.%20We%20visited%20a%20boutique%20seaside%20town%20and%20stayed%20in%20a%20cute%20little%20cottage%20with%20incredible%20views%20of%20the%20bay.%20We%20booked%20massages%2C%20ate%20at%20a%20high-end%20restaurant%2C%20and%20had%20a%20few%20drinks%20at%20a%