for%20each%20business.%20We%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-transparency-parents-talk-money-with-kids-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eshare%20financials%20transparently%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20leverage%20technology%2C%20and%20share%20information%20or%20ideas%20religiously.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20one%20of%20us%20is%20frustrated%20or%20confused%2C%20we%20say%20so%20early%2C%20before%20it%20becomes%20a%20bigger%20problem.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20level%20of%20candor%20has%20kept%20our%20relationships%20strong%20even%20through%20high-stress%20moments%2C%20like%20launching%20WealthRabbit%20the%20same%20week%20one%20of%20our%20co-founders%20suddenly%20died.%20We%20didn't%20have%20the%20luxury%20of%20falling%20apart.%20We%20had%20to%20keep%20the%20business%20moving%2C%20support%20our%20team%2C%20and%20honor%20his%20legacy%20by%20executing%20the%20vision.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20those%20moments%2C%20communication%20isn't%20just%20about%20keeping%20the%20business%20on%20track%3B%20it's%20about%20preserving%20the%20relationship.%20We're%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-flags-bad-business-partner-co-founder-startup-relationship-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebusiness%20partners%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20yes.%20But%20we're%20also%20brothers%2C%20and%20when%20things%20get%20hard%20(and%20they%20do)%2C%20that%20bond%20is%20what%20gets%20us%20through.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cdeaf5d8-be04-4e83-83e6-b82136e10b3d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20scale%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20it%3B%20build%20with%20purpose%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere's%20a%20myth%20in%20entrepreneurship%20that%20bigger%20is%20always%20better.%20That%20if%20you're%20not%20chasing%20the%20next%20round%2C%20the%20next%20product%20launch%2C%20or%20the%20next%20market%2C%20you're%20falling%20behind.%20That's%20not%20how%20we%20operate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe're%20building%20businesses%20that%20matter%20to%20us%20%E2%80%94%20ones%20that%20support%20our%20families%2C%20serve%20our%20clients%2C%20and%20solve%20real%20problems.%20BNA%20gives%20us%20the%20opportunity%20to%20work%20with%20large%20institutions%2C%20individuals%2C%20and%20business%20owners%20we%20genuinely%20care%20about.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20that%20experience%2C%20WealthRabbit%20was%20born%20out%20of%20a%20pain%20point%20we%20saw%20every%20tax%20season%3A%20small%20business%20owners%20asked%20for%20help%20setting%20up%20retirement%20plans%2C%20and%20we%20did%20all%20the%20legwork%20%E2%80%94%20for%20free%20%E2%80%94%20while%20traditional%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-does-a-financial-advisor-do%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efinancial%20advisors%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20collected%20the%20assets%20and%20the%20fees.%20We%20knew%20there%20had%20to%20be%20a%20better%20way%2C%20so%20we%20built%20one.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEvery%20major%20move%2C%20whether%20it's%20launching%20a%20new%20product%20or%20opening%20a%20new%20office%2C%20gets%20filtered%20through%20that%20lens.%20Do%20we%20both%20believe%20in%20it%3F%20Does%20it%20move%20us%20closer%20to%20our%20vision%3F%20Is%20it%20something%20we'd%20still%20be%20proud%20of%20five%20years%20from%20now%3F%20If%20the%20answer%20isn't%20yes%2C%20we%20don't%20do%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERunning%20a%20business%20with%20your%20sibling%20isn't%20easy%2C%20but%20with%20mutual%20respect%2C%20clear%20roles%2C%20open%20communication%2C%20and%20shared%20values%2C%20it%20can%20be%20a%20powerful%20force.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EJason%20Ackerman%2C%20CPA%2C%20CFP%2C%20CGMA%2C%20is%20the%20cofounder%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wealthrabbit.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EWealthRabbit%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3Eand%20managing%20partner%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bnacpa.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EBNA%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%20tax%20and%20wealth%20advisory%20firm%20based%20in%20North%20Carolina.%20Connect%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fjasonlackerman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrothers-own-companies-together-rules-swear-by-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754827621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6894d8afcfc04e97619b0577%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrothers-own-companies-together-rules-swear-by-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Running%20a%20business%20with%20my%20brother%20isn't%20easy.%20We%20implemented%20three%20rules%20to%20help%20us%20avoid%20conflict.%20Most%20importantly%2C%20we%20overcommunicate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jason%20Ackerman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrothers-own-companies-together-rules-swear-by-2025-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TVS%20Supply%20Chain%20Solutions%20Q1%20results%3A%20Profit%20rises%20to%20%E2%82%B971.16%20crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754826860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fquarterly-results%2Ftvs-supply-chain-solutions-q1-resul