ndia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-06T091445.064_11zon-1754451901-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-06T091445.064_11zon-1754451901-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-06T091445.064_11zon-1754451901-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-06T091445.064_11zon-1754451901-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-482241%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20foundation%20has%20reached%20over%2072%2C000%20children%2C%20changing%20how%20they%20learn%20by%20connecting%20them%20directly%20to%20the%20soil%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-year%20curriculum%20is%20designed%20for%20students%20in%20Classes%203%20to%205.%20SowGood%20also%20offers%20hands-on%20workshops%20for%20students%20of%20all%20ages%2C%20ensuring%20every%20child%20gets%20to%20engage%20with%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20is%20already%20visible.%20Lila%2C%20now%20a%20sustainability%20enthusiast%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20I%20thought%20farming%20was%20just%20dirt%20and%20bugs.%20But%20after%20resowing%20seeds%20three%20or%20four%20times%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F471133%2Flow-maintenance-monsoon-plants-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinally%20seeing%20them%20grow%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20sense%20of%20victory.%20It%20taught%20me%20patience%20and%20to%20never%20give%20up.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20convinced%20my%20family%20to%20stop%20using%20foil%20to%20wrap%20food