ains%20in%20detail%2C%20%E2%80%9CLike%20other%20crops%20of%20wheat%20and%20vegetables%2C%20we%20do%20not%20have%20a%20seed%20for%20mushrooms.%20It%20is%20a%20fungus%20which%20is%20manufactured%20in%20hygienic%20conditions%20in%20a%20lab.%20We%20require%20a%20tissue%20culture%20and%20mother%20spawn%20to%20multiply%20this%20fungus%20and%20get%20more%20spawns%20for%20commercialisation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-1705068160.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shanker%20officially%20launched%20his%20company%20which%20he%20runs%20along%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20Kanchan%20Meena.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-1705068160.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-1705068160-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-1705068160-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-1705068160-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-1705068160-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338238%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShanker%20officially%20launched%20his%20company%20which%20he%20runs%20along%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20Kanchan%20Meena.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20farmers%20take%20a%20shortcut%20and%20keep%20multiplying%20spawns%20using%20the%20commercial%20spawns%2C%20instead%20of%20preparing%20a%20different%20tissue%20culture%20and%20mother%20spawn.%20This%20reduces%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20spawns%20and%20ma