%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20answers%20we%20are%20looking%20for%20are%20present%20in%20traditional%20farming.%20I%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20efforts%20of%20my%20forefathers%20and%20father%20in%20building%20this%20farm%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20waste.%20Farmers%20have%20been%20practising%20soil%20conservation%20and%20balancing%20the%20ecosystem%20for%20ages.%20I%20use%20their%20knowledge%20with%20a%20small%20twist%20of%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saravanan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20making%20the%20fertilisers%20manually%20is%20a%20time-consuming%20process%2C%20he%20installed%20a%20biodigester%2C%20which%20produces%20seven%20times%20the%20output%20that%20was%20being%20produced%20earlier.%20All%20the%20waste%20generated%20in%20the%20cow%20shed%20is%20sent%20to%20the%20fermentation%20chamber%2C%20generating%20almost%207%2C000%20litres%20of%20fertilisers%20daily%2C%20as%20per%20the%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC5IhIfZSWFr%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC5IhIfZSWFr%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC5IhIfZSWFr%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Deesan%20Organic%20Farms%20(%40deesan_organic_farms)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20fertilisers%20are%20mixed%20and%20applied%20to%20the%20plantations%20every%2015%20days.%20The%20vermicompost%20unit%20generates%20almost%201.5%20tonnes%20of%20vermicompost%20every%20month.%20A%20biogas%20unit%20utilises%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20cow%20dung.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20these%20machines%2C%20Saravanan%20focused%20on%20creating%20a%20microclimate%20while%20generating%20more%20income%20through%20intercropping.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20farm%20had%20monocropping%20with%201%2C650%20coconut%20trees.%20Saravanan%20added%20banana%2C%20nutmeg%2C%20areca%20nut%20amidst%20the%20coconut%20trees.%20Besides%20this%2C%20he%20added%20guava%20and%20papaya%20on%20open%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20has%20created%20biodiversity%2C%20giving%20us%20financial%20and%20biological%20benefits%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20creating%20a%20self-sustained%20farm%2C%20the%20next%20step%20was%20to%20create%20a%20market%20for%20the%20products.%20For%20this%2C%20Krishnasudha%20stepped%20in%20and%20suggested%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356941%2Forganic-farming-mba-grad-earns-crores-earthy-tales-delhi-ncr-deepak-sabharwal-rajasthan-farm-pesticides%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evalue-added%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20coconut%20oil%20and%20%3Cem%3Eghee%3C%2Fem%3E.%20They%20set%20up%20a%20production%20unit%20on%20their%20farm%20itself%20with%20a%20solar%20dryer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20day%20has%20been%20a%20learning%20experience%20here.%20There%20is%20lesser%20stress%20as%20compared%20to%20a%20corporate%20job%20with%20the%20added%20benefit%20of%20serving%20good%20products%20to%20customers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Deesan%20Farms%20makes%20a%20tonne%20of%20coconut%20oil%20and%20250%20kg%20of%20%3Cem%3Eghee%20%3C%2Fem%3Eper%20week%2C%20claims%20Saravanan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurning%20youngsters%E2%80%99%20interest%20to%20farming%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Saravanan%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20knowledge%20about%20farming%20thanks%20to%20his%20parents%20and%20grandparents%2C%20he%20attended%20a%20natural%20farming%20course.%20He%20says%20that%20this%20helped%20him%20with%20better%20ways%20of%20creating%20manure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Students%20learning%20farming%20at%20Deesan%20Farms%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357939%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EStudents%20learning%20farming%20at%20Deesan%20Farms%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20farm%2C%20named%20after%20his%20father%2C%20Jagadeeshan%20is%20today%20a%20model%20farm%2C%20visited%20by%20thousands.%20He%20has%20also%20been%20recognised%20by%20the%20Kerala%20Government%20for%20his%20efforts%20in%20organic%20farming.%20He%20has%20been%20awarded%20the%20Kera%20Kesari%20Award%20in%202017%2C%20the%20Yuva%20Kesari%20Award%20in%202019%2C%20and%20the%20Akshayasree%20Award%202022-23%20for%20Best%20Organic%20Farming%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20farm%20was%20set%20up%20and%20started%20running%20smoothly%2C%20he%20was%20filled%20with%20the%20desire%20to%20share%20his%20knowledge%20with%20the%20next%20generation.%20%E2%80%9CMerely%20one%20person%20practising%20a%20sustainable%20model%20of%20farming%20is%20of%20no%20good%20if%20that%20information%20is%20not%20shared.%20I%20wanted%20to%20educate%20other%20farmers%20and%20students%20about%20healthy%20ways%20to%20grow%20food%2C%20consume%20food%20and%20practice%20farming%20that%20is%20beneficial%20to%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaravanan%20conducts%20classes%20for%20the%20Kerala%20Government%20under%20the%20Bhartiya%20Prakritik%20Krishi%20Paddhti%20(BPKP)%20and%20the%20Paramparagath%20Krishi%20Vikas%20Yojana%20(PKVY)%20scheme.%20With%20at%20least%20three%20classes%20per%20week%2C%20he%20claims%20to%20have%20educated%20over%2015%2C000%20farmers%20and%20students%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESreedhu%20P%2C%20agricultural%20officer%2C%20Perumatty%2C%20says%20that%20Saravanan%E2%80%99s%20farm%20is%20a%20perfect%20example%20of%20how%20an%20organic%20farm%20should%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan33-1721657916-500x734.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saravanan%20turned%20his%20family%20farm%20around%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan33-1721657916-500x734.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan33-1721657916-20